posts.title: Wobbly Life
posts.description: Wobbly Life is a lively open-world Read More...
posts.written:
Wobbly Life is a lively open-world physics-based sandbox. Explore Wobbly Island with your friends, discover fun locations filled with minigames and dynamic toys. 


Be hard-working wobbly and work around town in various roles to earn cash to own properties and purchase/customize new clothes and vehicles.
